22 agency, the law enforcement agency shall not, except as otherwise
23 required by federal or state law, keep or make a record of the
24 investigation or the imposition of punitive action after the record is
25 required to be removed from the administrative file.
26 4. A law enforcement agency may reassign a peace officer
